    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The application of a poultice, which is a substance with a soft, absorbent, or pasty consistency. For cleaning, the poultice is applied to an area in order to draw out a stain or remove other substances in a controlled manner. Poultices are also used in medical applications.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
